{"tid":273792,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"求一套H漫","createTime":"2017-06-07T00:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T07:11:37.000Z","uid":30745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b89dd4b841be54d9abb234d352827ad7e5293b8","tid":273792,"uid":30745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:27:04.000Z","msg":"個故事內容係一隻社畜翻左屋企，佢老婆問佢要食飯，沖涼定要佢，當佢老婆想同社畜kiss果時佢煎緊條魚燶左<br />\n結果佢地最後入左浴室沖涼，老婆好消沉，社畜安慰佢仲可以食茶泡飯，點知佢老婆就想哭咁嘅樣同主角講唔好討厭佢，之後就嚟正劇<br />\n之後入室繼續果時，佢老婆太忘我如果搞到主角條頸留低吻痕，之後又哭哭地嘅叫主角唔好討厭佢，然後又入正劇<br />\n最後主角決定聽日請假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求全能嘅動物台巴打比個名我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d941dcc59deb73b199d48f8b1ee3c56b133b8c","tid":273792,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:28:41.000Z","msg":"打少啲飛機啦"},{"pid":"c2dd2b6d8f1e49cb574a6843f5706021dee11d7e","tid":273792,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:29:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打少啲飛機啦</blockquote><br />\n又唔係拎嚟打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1879822c4f1f1a1c702e97cc584d799f859b80cd","tid":273792,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:37:30.000Z","msg":"咁搞笑"},{"pid":"51eb6298f1055fd90bf2342ef0c3b44d7a263889","tid":273792,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打少啲飛機啦</blockquote><br />\n又唔係拎嚟打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係打飛機我就無謂幫你啦"},{"pid":"e5232ca0176d24fb2b3b312993ac549f746db0ac","tid":273792,"uid":40269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:44:43.000Z","msg":"個款咁像ntr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672d5b6fee2ca9ed098b34d0677e057cb323aefb","tid":273792,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite